        "generateUrl": "https://knowledge.spinify.com/help/how-to-integrate-with-the-spinify-api",
        "setup": "Log into [MySpinify](https://my.spinify.com/login), then go to **Settings → Integrations** and choose **Connect** on the API Integration to generate and copy your API key. Spinify's help docs say revoke/reset/new keys are handled by contacting Spinify through the in-app chat in MySpinify.",
